CR - 25030013 has been raised To fix the response time in the E1MRService.

Code modifications are done in CR - 25030013

Log db initial save and update logdb code has been removed

Branch and teller validations has been removed

Framework aggregator removed and cpu memory configurations increased for high throughput.

Due to techops approval and service made in java CR 25030013 has been cancelled.





